decoworld.model.world.safehouse.furniture

Class TrophyCabinet

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.model.world.safehouse.furniture.TrophyCabinet

  • public class TrophyCabinet
extends java.lang.Object
    This will store a player's current list of achievements to be displayed in a trophy cabinet in their safehouse Invariant: achievements != null (can, however, be empty list) achievements does not contain null list, each list in achievements contains 5 non-null strings user != null, user is a valid user in the game
